                    <article itemprop="text"><p>We do, for both incoming and outgoing calls. Incoming is easy enough, as
                            it is essentially using your contact list and known callers to identify the call. For
                            outgoing calls—to have your business name show up when you call others—we offer free support
                            and entry into the CNAME database which controls that.</p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
